{"tid":1807200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立陶宛前議員豎十字架撐港人","createTime":"2020-01-01T16:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T16:56:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1090a582db44abbeb477da56908fe3047efc6bc5","tid":1807200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200101/COGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200101%2FCOGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI%2F&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=1a2a16dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200101%2FCOGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI%2F&h=24223917\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200101/COGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n立陶宛前議員豎十字架撐港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立陶宛名勝十字架山（The Hill of Crosses）早前被發現部份寫上支持香港抗爭的十字架遭中國遊客扔丟，又有藍絲在紀念先人的十字架上塗寫侮辱香港人是「甴曱」的字句。事件引起當地政府及民間關注，立陶宛外長林克維丘斯（Linas Linkevicius）日前發表聲明譴責行為可恥。立陶宛議會前議員、立陶宛基督教民主黨前副主席Mantas Adomenas周一更在十字架山上架設聲援香港的十字架，並揚言未來會有更多行動以示支持香港抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警旺角放新年第一彈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200101/large/1577811945_0be3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200101%2Flarge%2F1577811945_0be3.gif&h=7d79e4b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立陶宛前議員Mantas Adomenas（左）在十字架山上豎立聲援香港的十字架。fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預告行動陸續有來<br />\n<br />\nAdomenas在facebook展示數張相片，顯示一個寫着「Free Hong Kong. Democracy Now」（解放香港，實現民主）字句的十字架正豎立在十字架山上。他說這個行動只是第一步，「還會陸續有來&mdash;標言、紀念碑、示威、政治行動及實質措施，顯示立陶宛支持香港」。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，行動是為了香港的自由民主、為了在前線抗爭的勇敢香港人。他說：「昔日蘇聯嘗試消滅十字架山，結果這座山留下，蘇聯走了。中共企圖消滅香港人在十字架山的祝願，而為香港而設的十字架現在重現這裏，我肯定，共產黨的圖謀已經失敗。」"},{"pid":"1155c54f46b50850c75add9bc28ddc28164a8eaf","tid":1807200,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0304d431c7ee25671bbb448b85fe4a6755d911","tid":1807200,"uid":189157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WE CONNECT</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a2d7172706765c957dcfebb1dcd1e324c7f0c5","tid":1807200,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee74a2377804ce20c6ae3b83a9af6db92cfd36f6","tid":1807200,"uid":293673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2365181db1a31e76fec2cbaa73a44d56b69edcc4","tid":1807200,"uid":20979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望世界有更多地方聽到香港人聲音"},{"pid":"569f86e1e5d6ef0477c01069eb425eb3865f0f0c","tid":1807200,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:38:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\nConnected<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下一個<br />\n梵蒂岡<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"95dc43d2d0c3a6461064581a8466ae183599a03f","tid":1807200,"uid":241742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"大家上facebook多謝下Adomenas"},{"pid":"5a951deed32612e729435440f072b6a9b4b6fd72","tid":1807200,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"幫手叫外國一齊整個黃色經濟圈 要外國扯制中國貨"},{"pid":"c5dd6aafc9339ff587d42ec7c7bec7f262c7d591","tid":1807200,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［急尋人！］</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月1日 銅鑼灣citibank前被捕手足去向 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807139</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求幫推"},{"pid":"e5c93bd6123d9bc3e926157985866d257a5a5309","tid":1807200,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"好cs 一個小粉紅令到成個國家有唔同行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthank you sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a5656b27e854d2df9095f650cb82b3a48f1809","tid":1807200,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4bbc788aed644778dff18e40bb3600b22fd9cc9","tid":1807200,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2a5656b27e854d2df9095f650cb82b3a48f1809","tid":1807200,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1090a582db44abbeb477da56908fe3047efc6bc5","tid":1807200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200101/COGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200101%2FCOGZDJ2KB737QAQTNRUGMUCXWI%2F&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=1a2a16dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=htt